{
  "stem": "10588.11",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] [NON-ENGLISH  SPEECH] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'96.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'96.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, I was born to religious Jewish parents-- Simo and Eljo Frajman, in a small town Ciechanow of Poland, located about 90 kilometers north of Warsaw, during Passover, April 15th, 1926.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the oldest of three children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had   a younger brother Srulek, a little sister Zeisel, and my maternal widowed grandmother, Chaye Sure Zebrah lived with us and helped to raise me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My first home was in Ciechanow, Poland, [POLISH] not far from where the soldiers used to be stationed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason I remember so exactly this is because I remember when I was a little girl, my father of blessed memory used to say, you know, Itkalo, the whole army that is stationed here can never hurt you as much as you can hurt yourself, when you don't behave morally and ethically.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have extremely mixed emotions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have wonderful memories till the age of 13.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have horrible memories from the age of 13 to 19.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because till the age of 13 was my world before Nazi destruction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From age 13 till 19 was my world during Nazi destruction and afterwards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my oldest memory is of my home, because we lived in two homes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the first one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't own this home, we rented it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was not far from the stations, where the soldiers were stationed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was-- I remember it exactly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The entrance where we used to go was from the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the back, there was a huge, huge field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go out on one flight of steps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to live there with the members of my family that I already  mentioned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to play here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of my closest friends of non-Jewish friends was a girl named Halinka.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to have wonderful times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She would come to our house, and my mother always treated her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I came to her house, her mother tried to treat me with food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, I would not eat all the food in the house, because we kept a kosher home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Halinka once cried and said, Itkalo, that's not fair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I eat in your home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why don't you eat in mine?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came and said that to my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said, Itkalo, we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have to respect Halinka's holidays and customs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we cannot eat everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can have fruit there or vegetables, but you cannot have meat in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Halinka and I were very good friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to play together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember one special incident when we were little.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We use to tell each other how we celebrate holidays-- how we celebrate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother once explained to me-- she said, you can share your holidays.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can visit to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But just like you cannot celebrate her birthday, because she's born on a different day, so she cannot celebrate yours.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you can share.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She wanted to point out that I should tolerate her religion and her people and respect them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But at the same token, I should observe my own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because this is who I am and who I represent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could I describe my room?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in every little detail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember in the kitchen we had-- there was a square in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had an iron ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You pulled it up to go down to a dark root cellar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason why they called it the root cellar because we didn't have electricity in those days, so we didn't have refrigeration and all the modern appliances.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we would keep our food-- the perishable food to keep cold-- in the root cellar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember that when I looked through the window, I used to see many times the soldiers marching.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I played with children, because here I didn't live till age 13.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just lived the earliest years here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I remember there was an attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We used to go up to the attic as children, to play there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what I remember is in the back of the house, there was a huge field.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was so open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I felt so free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I used, like a child-- I used to look like this and pretend I'm a bird and run and play.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the winter, I remember when it was the first snow, I would run out and lay down in the snow, to leave a mark.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as a child, played all kinds of different kinds of games with children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also the oldest memories I remember-- the holidays with my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember the interaction with my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
